    "rationale": "Despite the overall COU2 decision of Not Accepted at MRL 5, the credibility assessment package itself is accepted as a complete and valid assessment artifact. All 13 credibility factors are evaluated or explicitly flagged as not-assessed with documented rationale. Monte Carlo UQ is linked for the primary hemolysis prediction result. Note: the mesh sensitivity validation result characterizes blood rheology variability qualitatively by engineering judgement only; no structured UQ node is linked for that result, leaving aleatory uncertainty from inter-donor blood property variation uncharacterized in the structured evidence record.",
